                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The information set forth above is derived from the accounts of the dinner in
                        <persName corresp="#p_ACHESONDG1">Acheson</persName>, <hi rend="italic"
                        >Present at the Creation</hi>, page 627 and <persName
                        corresp="#p_ACHESONDG1">Acheson</persName>, <hi rend="italic">Sketches from
                        Life</hi>, pages 111–113. No official record of the discussions during the
                    dinner have been found, and presumably no substantive matters were taken up.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
